{'id': 10307499203, 'title': "Women's Black Mesh Hoodie", 'handle': 'womens-black-mesh-hoodie', 'description': '

Who says covering up can't be fun? Our sporty black mesh\xa0hoodie is perfect to wear when you're heading out to the beach\xa0before or\xa0after the gym. The hood also\xa0give a little more coverage when you want to take a break from the sun while still keeping you cool.

Features:
  • Short sleeve\xa0hoodie with our signature Amade “A” panel in\xa0front
  • Made with lightweight breathable mesh\xa0that\xa0keeps you cool
  • Double kangaroo pockets
  • Available in black or white
Product Details:
  • 100% poly mesh
  • Hand wash cold water
  • Made in the USA

{'id': 10417825539, 'title': '2 Inch White Mesh Shorts', 'handle': '2-inch-white-mesh-shorts', 'description': '

Cover up in these sporty men’s white\xa0mesh shorts on your way to or\xa0from\xa0a relaxing day at the beach or pool. These mesh shorts not only have subtle front hidden pockets, but are extremely breathable as well. They also have an enhanced comfort due to the 4 way stretch lining in each style. Also available in 4" inseam.

Features:

  • Elastic Waistband
  • Loop-chain pocket for your locker key
  • 2” inseam
  • Lined with 4 way stretch nylon
  • Metal triangle logo on left bottom
  • Available in black and white

Product Details:

  • 100% polyester
  • Hand wash cold water
  • Made in USA
